{
  "message": "feat(embeddings): add vector embeddings infrastructure for semantic search\n\nImplements brenner_bot-ukd1.1: Create Vector Embeddings for Brenner Corpus\n\nChanges:\n- Add embeddings.test.ts with 12 comprehensive tests\n- Add embeddings generation to prebuild script in package.json\n- Add embeddings.json to .gitignore (generated at build time)\n- Install @huggingface/transformers for future ML-based embeddings\n\nThe embedding module uses a deterministic FNV-1a hash-based approach:\n- 384-dimensional sparse vectors\n- Cosine similarity for matching\n- findSimilar() for semantic search\n- Works client-side without API calls\n\nGenerated 674 entries:\n- 292 transcript chunks\n- 117 distillation chunks\n- 261 quote entries\n- 4 operator entries\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
